                    <description>
&lt;p&gt;I saw this entry in the forums and I&apos;m having the same problem, setting maxReconnectAttempts to a specific value does not stop the infinite loop of &quot;Waiting for transport to reconnect&quot; from occuring.&lt;/p&gt;

